\pc \bd 302\bd*

\s Bwana, sasa uruhusu watu
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Bwana, sasa uruhusu watu wako kwenda kwao\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Umetufikisha hapa, umetubariki sana\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Umekusanyika nasi, kwenda nasi kwa mungini.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Tunakushukuru sana kwa baraka yako kubwa\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Ndani ya kitabu chako umetufundisha roho\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Tukikwenda tukumbuke Neno tuliolipata.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Umepanda mbegu yako, sasa uitie maji\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Hivi tutazaa matunda, utukuzwe ndani yetu\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Utuchunge hata siku tutakapomwona Yesu.\bd*
